      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To promote training and employment for public housing residents in home-based health services so such residents can provide Medicaid covered home-based health services to elderly and disabled persons receiving public housing assistance from the Department of Housing and Urban Development.</title>
